  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello. Hi, Peridot.",
      "zh": "哈囉。嗨，Peridot。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。やあ、ペリドット。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Steven, can you hear me?",
      "zh": "Steven，你能聽到我嗎？",
      "ja": "スティーブン、聞こえる？",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can hear you hear me.",
      "zh": "我能聽到你，聽到我嗎？",
      "ja": "聞こえるよ、僕の声が聞こえる？",
      "time": "00:00:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can hear you.",
      "zh": "我能聽到你。",
      "ja": "聞こえるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can hear you.",
      "zh": "我能聽到你。",
      "ja": "聞こえるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-huh, I work to skip it, Peridot.",
      "zh": "嗯哼，我努力跳過它，Peridot。",
      "ja": "うん、うまくいったよ、ペリドット。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Steven?",
      "zh": "Steven？",
      "ja": "スティーブン？",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, Peridot.",
      "zh": "嗨，Peridot。",
      "ja": "やあ、ペリドット。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Steven?",
      "zh": "Steven？",
      "ja": "スティーブン？",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha.",
      "zh": "哈哈哈哈哈哈。",
      "ja": "はははははは。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Behold.",
      "zh": "看這個。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My resourceful genius.",
      "zh": "我這個足智多謀的天才。",
      "ja": "僕の機転の利く天才ぶりを。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I figured out how to get life by in the barn.",
      "zh": "我想出怎麼在穀倉裡活下去的方法。",
      "ja": "納屋で生き延びる方法を見つけたんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The connection is fast enough to stream camp timing hearts",
      "zh": "連線速度快到可以串流露營時間的心跳",
      "ja": "接続はキャンプのタイミングの心拍をストリーミングできるほど速い",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "in all 1,080.",
      "zh": "全1080p畫質。",
      "ja": "フル1080でね。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Peace.",
      "zh": "和平。",
      "ja": "平和だ。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It took me a while.",
      "zh": "花了我一陣子。",
      "ja": "ちょっと時間がかかったけど。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But let me tell you how I did it.",
      "zh": "但讓我告訴你我是怎麼做到的。",
      "ja": "でもどうやったか教えてあげる。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So let it go through.",
      "zh": "所以讓它通過。",
      "ja": "だから通してみたんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Peridot?",
      "zh": "Peridot？",
      "ja": "ペリドット？",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So there I was, face to face with one of those big.",
      "zh": "我就那樣，面對著其中一個大東西。",
      "ja": "そこにいたんだ、大きなやつと向かい合って。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Peridot, you're breaking up.",
      "zh": "Peridot，你的訊號斷斷續續。",
      "ja": "ペリドット、声が途切れてる。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Running for my life with nothing but a f-",
      "zh": "拼命逃命，手上只有一把f-",
      "ja": "命からがら逃げてた、ただのf-しか持たずに",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And then it bit me!",
      "zh": "然後它咬了我！",
      "ja": "そしたら噛まれたんだ！",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And now the wife, I work perfectly.",
      "zh": "現在這個工作完美無缺。",
      "ja": "そして今は、ワイヤレスが完璧に動いてる。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What did you do today?",
      "zh": "你今天做了什麼？",
      "ja": "今日は何をしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I learned how to do this.",
      "zh": "我學會了怎麼做這個。",
      "ja": "これのやり方を覚えたんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lapis, get over here.",
      "zh": "Lapis，過來這裡。",
      "ja": "ラピス、こっちに来て。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is that Steven?",
      "zh": "那是Steven嗎？",
      "ja": "あれはスティーブン？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, Steven, what happened?",
      "zh": "哦，Steven，發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "ああ、スティーブン、どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, you guys, it's fine.",
      "zh": "哦，你們，沒事的。",
      "ja": "ああ、みんな、大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just-",
      "zh": "只是-",
      "ja": "ただ-",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How did he get trapped in there?",
      "zh": "他怎麼被困在那裡的？",
      "ja": "どうやってそこに閉じ込められたの？",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why are you doing something?",
      "zh": "你為什麼要做什麼？",
      "ja": "なんで何かしてるの？",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lapis, relax.",
      "zh": "Lapis，冷靜。",
      "ja": "ラピス、落ち着いて。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's my communication pad.",
      "zh": "這是我的通訊板。",
      "ja": "これは僕の通信パッドだ。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who did that to you?",
      "zh": "誰對你做了那個？",
      "ja": "誰がそんなことをしたの？",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Steven, I'll get you out of there.",
      "zh": "Steven，我會把你救出來。",
      "ja": "スティーブン、助け出すよ。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's your gem on this thing.",
      "zh": "這是你在這東西上的寶石。",
      "ja": "これが君のジェムだ、この機械の上にある。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't-",
      "zh": "我找不到-",
      "ja": "見つからない-",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't find it.",
      "zh": "我找不到它。",
      "ja": "見つからないんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You must be inside.",
      "zh": "你一定在裡面。",
      "ja": "君は中にいるに違いない。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lapis.",
      "zh": "Lapis。",
      "ja": "ラピス。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just a screen.",
      "zh": "這只是一個螢幕。",
      "ja": "ただの画面だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop.",
      "zh": "停下。",
      "ja": "やめて。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, geez.",
      "zh": "喔，天哪。",
      "ja": "ああ、やれやれ。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, thank the stars.",
      "zh": "哦，感謝星星。",
      "ja": "ああ、星に感謝。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought you were a goner.",
      "zh": "我還以為你完了。",
      "ja": "君はもうダメかと思ったよ。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Step aside, Peridot.",
      "zh": "讓開，Peridot。",
      "ja": "どいて、ペリドット。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have to free him.",
      "zh": "我得救他出來。",
      "ja": "彼を助けなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lapis?",
      "zh": "Lapis？",
      "ja": "ラピス？",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll save you, Steven.",
      "zh": "我會救你，Steven。",
      "ja": "スティーブン、助けるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll save you like you saved me.",
      "zh": "我會像你救我一樣救你。",
      "ja": "君が僕を助けてくれたように、僕も君を助ける。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come down.",
      "zh": "下來。",
      "ja": "降りてきて。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop.",
      "zh": "停下。",
      "ja": "やめて。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm fine.",
      "zh": "我沒事。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Steven.",
      "zh": "Steven。",
      "ja": "スティーブン。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm here, okay.",
      "zh": "我在這裡，好嗎。",
      "ja": "ここにいるよ、わかった？",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry, Peridot.",
      "zh": "抱歉，Peridot。",
      "ja": "ごめんね、ペリドット。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just take it easy with that bat.",
      "zh": "那隻蝙蝠輕點。",
      "ja": "そのコウモリは優しく扱ってね。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, look.",
      "zh": "哦，看。",
      "ja": "ああ、見て。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's lion.",
      "zh": "是獅子。",
      "ja": "ライオンだ。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lion.",
      "zh": "獅子。",
      "ja": "ライオン。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lion.",
      "zh": "獅子。",
      "ja": "ライオン。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Be careful.",
      "zh": "小心點。",
      "ja": "気をつけて。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lion.",
      "zh": "獅子。",
      "ja": "ライオン。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That was Connie's laptop.",
      "zh": "那是Connie的筆記型電腦。",
      "ja": "あれはコニーのノートパソコンだ。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lion.",
      "zh": "獅子。",
      "ja": "ライオン。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He should really be more careful with other people's stuff.",
      "zh": "他真的應該對別人的東西更小心。",
      "ja": "他は他人の物をもっと大事に扱うべきだ。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    }
  ]
}